title: Warriors, nicknames, Patriots, young coaches, & the Herd Hierarchy
itunes:title: Warriors, nicknames, Patriots, young coaches, & the Herd Hierarchy
description:
Colin discusses who will most likely be leaving the Golden State Warriors first, why he dislikes nicknames, why people hate the New England Patriots, why young coaches are getting people fired, and the Herd Hierarchy. Guests include Albert Breer, Rob Parker, and Logan Ryan.
